
Current plans for creating the Dialog infrastructure:

GUI widgets
>> A Jquery plugin question widget (questions with 0-5 answers)
>> A full page questionair for multiple questions with variable number of answers
>> Phonegap based TTS/ASR question widget
>> Facebook messages/Wall implementation

Other media
>> VoiceXML generator for questions
>> Tropo (www.tropo.com) based question voice setup

Dialog/Document server
>> JS local document server  (node.js?)
>> GAE dialog server

